                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The main uncertainties came from the",
                "detection efficiency calibration, the statistical",
                "ones of characteristic gamma-ray peaks, and the",
                "uncertainties of other parameters."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
