            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The isotope 134I of which characteristic gamma-rays",
                "were detected in the gamma-spectrum was concluded to",
                "be originated from 134Te decay. According to the",
                "cascade deduction formulism, the cross-section of",
                "232Th(n,f)134I was estimated to be below a value",
                " (~5.7E-3 mb) refered to the Minimal Detectable",
                "Activity (MDA) with the gamma measurements."
              ]
            }
          ],
